title: Inc. India - July 2014
description:
Inc. India - July 2014
 True PDF | 48 pages | English | 6.1 MB

Inc. India is the Indian edition of the American magazine Inc., your monthly guide to running a successful business. We chronicle the growth of the country's most exciting young companies, bringing to you stories of their success, failures and the grit and frustration that go into building these.
